Entities.Name: Application
Entities.Description: Entity to store application details including fields related to applicant status, scores, and other metadata.

Fields.Name: ApplicationNumber
Fields.Description: Text field for unique application numbers.

Fields.Name: FullName
Fields.Description: Text field for the applicant's full name.

Fields.Name: Age
Fields.Description: Integer field for the applicant's age.

Fields.Name: Email
Fields.Description: Text field for the applicant's email address.

Fields.Name: Phone
Fields.Description: Text field for the applicant's phone number.

Fields.Name: JobTitle
Fields.Description: Text field for the job title the applicant is applying for.

Fields.Name: CVObjectKey
Fields.Description: Text field for the key associated with the applicant's CV in the system.

Fields.Name: Status
Fields.Description: Text field representing the current status of the application.

Fields.Name: Match
Fields.Description: Boolean field indicating whether the applicant matches the job requirements.

Fields.Name: Score
Fields.Description: Integer field representing the applicant's score.

Fields.Name: ReasonsJson
Fields.Description: Long text field that stores reasons related to the application in JSON format.

Fields.Name: CreatedOn
Fields.Description: DateTime field to capture the creation timestamp of the application.

Entities.Name: SystemUser
Entities.Description: Contains Automation Cloud users and groups that have ever had roles assigned, or accessed Data Service
